@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
title Verification in layers (cheapest to strongest)

start
:write the validator;
:unit tests
(the bugs you thought of);
if (pass?) then (no)
  :fix; back to tests;
  detach
else (yes)
endif
:property-based testing
(thousands of random inputs
against invariants:
"no tx extracts more than deposited");
if (invariants hold?) then (no)
  :shrink counterexample; fix;
  detach
else (yes)
endif
:professional audit
(line-by-line review,
attack-surface analysis,
testnet penetration testing);
:optional: formal verification
(prove a property for all inputs);
:deploy to mainnet
only after these layers pass;
stop
@enduml
